Tentative calendar
January 4- Branches and commissions wind up elections
January 11- Branches, commissions and teams send in names of two delegates, one votes and one is alternate.
January 15- All national office aspiring candidates to have returned forms to the election panel
January 23- National Elections day
January 30 & 31- Pre-season tournament
February 6- National leagues- 1st leg
February 19-25 - Afrobasket qualifiers W3- men, Venue-TBD
March 2021- Africa Club Championships women, Egypt
April- Anoca Youth Games Under-18, Egypt
May/June- Afrobasket women qualifiers, Venue-TBD
August- Afrobasket men final tour, Rwanda
November- National senior 3x3 Africa, Kampala
National U17 3x3 Africa Kampala TBD
National U18 3x3 Africa TBD
